message.content: Yeza, ndiyakuncedisa ngokwenza inkqubo yokwazi ukulawula iidron. Ndifanele ndiyakwazi ukukwazi amazwi athethwe ngokuqhekezelwa kweeidron. Ndifune ukwazisa amasashele amaningi akuwe, ngoko ke ndiyakuncedisa ngokuphendula kwakho ngolwimi lwesiXhosa. Ndicela ufake iindlela ezihamba ngazo ukuphendula kwakho ngolwimi lwesiXhosa.
